Draw the board
```
match
  [@tiles player: player-tile box: box-tile wall: wall-tile goal: goal-tile]
  [@board height width]
  [#cell x y]
  tile = if [@player x y] then player-tile
         else if [#wall x y] then wall-tile
         else if [#box x y] then box-tile
         else if [#goal x y] then goal-tile
         else ""
  color = if [#goal x y] then "cyan"
            else "white"
bind
  [#div sort: 1 style:
    [font-size: "24px"
     text-align: "center"]
    children:
      [#div sort: y children:
        [#div sort: x style: [color
                              line-height: "24px"
                              width: "24px"
                              height: "24px"
                              display: "inline-block"]
         text: tile]]]
```
